high_descs: walk straight towards the tv, turn right after you pass the sofa, turn right again and head towards the sofa, stand in front of the sofa
locate the apple on the sofa
pick up the apple, turn right and walk straight ahead into the bathroom, turn left at the sink and stop in front of it
put the apple next to the brown cutting board, turn on the faucet,fill the sink with water, turn off the faucet, put the apple in the water to rinse it off, let out the water, grab the apple
step back, turn left and leave the bathroom, turn left to avoid the sofa, turn right, walk towards the table and microwave, stop in front of the table
open the microwave door, put the apple inside, to the left of the glass plate, close the microwave door
anns.task_desc: to clean the apple and put it in the microwave to thaw for a recipe

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sofa
Pick up apple from the sofa
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right
Place apple inside the sink and then take it out
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the microwave
anns.task_desc: Washing apple on the sink and placing it on microwave

high_descs: Go forward, after the sofa, turn right. When you reach the sofa, turn right.
Turn right, go straight ahead, when you reach the entrance, turn left. Turn right, enter the bathroom, when you reach the sink, turn left.
Place the apple in the washer on the right side, open the taps for 5 seconds. Close the taps. Grab the apple.
Turn left, go straight ahead, turn left at the exit, turn right, go straight ahead to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple on the left side, close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Wash an apple in a sink, place it in the microwave.
